channel.description: Hello, I just how two questions. How do you change the ranged strength of arrows in deltascape (specifically devolutioned base) and what do you have to add to client.java to get the globaldrops.cfg file to work? I noticed that there isn't a globaldrops method unlike the other .cfg files, but I don't know what I would put to get that work. Thank you for your time! =D
